casebody.data:
Ronald Bernard BRITTBEY, Appellant, v. Eve M. RILEY, Administrative Law Judge, Appellee. No. 02-4092. United States Court of Appeals, Eighth Circuit. Submitted March 21, 2003. Decided March 28, 2003.

Before MELLOY, FAGG, and SMITH, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Ronald Bernard Britt-Bey appeals the district court’s* preservice dismissal, without prejudice, of his civil lawsuit. Having carefully reviewed the record, we conclude dismissal was proper. Accordingly, we affirm. See 8th Cir. R. 47B.

The Honorable Catherine D. Perry, United States District Judge for the Eastern District of Missouri.
